UPDATE generic_inference_jobs
SET
  status = 'cancelled_by_system',
  retry_at = NULL,
  internal_debugging_failure_reason = 'reap_stale_fakeyou_jobs'
WHERE
  job_type != 'fal_queue'
  AND status IN (
    'pending',
    'started',
    'attempt_failed'
   )
   AND created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL 30 MINUTE
LIMIT 5000
